    # ks "Shhh, Nozomi... it's alright. It's appropriate for you to feel this way around me. Feeling so relaxed. So drowsy. So sleepy."
    ks "Shhh, Nozomi... todo está bien. Es apropiado sentirte de esta forma junto a mí. Sentirte tan relajada. Tan adormecida. Tan soñolienta."

# game/kyou 1.rpy:366
