    # "So far my penlight seems to be having the desired effect, having kept her attention all this time."
    "Hasta ahora la linterna parece tener un efecto grandioso, habiendo retenido su atención todo este tiempo."

# game/kyou 1.rpy:371
translate spanish Day1_Kyou_095fbb50:

    # "But now, thanks to my words I can see it's taking all her conscious will just to keep her eyelids from snapping completely shut."
    "Pero ahora, gracias a mis palabras, puedo ver que está usando toda su voluntad para evitar que sus párpados se cierren por completo."

# game/kyou 1.rpy:371
