    # ks "And that's exactly what we're doing right now. I'm helping you relax and have a nice break, and there's nothing wrong with that." with dissolve
    ks "Y eso es exactamente lo que estamos haciendo. Te ayudo a relajarte y tomar un lindo descanso, y no hay nada de malo en eso." with dissolve

# game/kyou 1.rpy:411
translate spanish Day1_Kyou_d6534108:

    # ks "As a matter of fact, that's exactly what you need. You're feeling so much more calm right now without all that tension weighing you down."
    ks "A decir verdad, es exactamente lo que necesitas. Te sientes mucho más calmada ahora sin el pesar de toda esa tensión."

# game/kyou 1.rpy:412
translate spanish Day1_Kyou_d675c492:

    # ks "Doesn't it feel nice to be so relaxed on your break with me?"
    ks "¿Acaso no se siente bien estar tan relajada en tu descanso conmigo?"

# game/kyou 1.rpy:413
translate spanish Day1_Kyou_91dc085e_2:

    # ncg "..."
    ncg "..."

# game/kyou 1.rpy:414
