    # "I hurriedly push my penlight back into my pocket, but I had been standing there in front of Nozomi with it still in my hand." with dissolve
    "Meto apresuradamente la linterna a mi bolsillo, pero estuve parado frente a Nozomi con ella en la mano." with dissolve

# game/kyou 1.rpy:464
translate spanish Day1_Kyou_597e54ab:

    # "She must have seen it."
    "Debe haberla visto."

# game/kyou 1.rpy:465
